{"tid":705183,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"「長文」其實諗返轉頭 C朗真係遇到唔少貴人 造就佢同美斯既分別","createTime":"2018-06-17T02:32:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-17T03:34:55.000Z","uid":5006,"like":47,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"00f5c4f5bfc0206f77deb65080719bcb66f90d4d","tid":705183,"uid":5006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T02:32:00.000Z","msg":"<strong>第一位費人：費格遜</strong><br />\nC朗自己都講過當費格遜老豆 <br />\n教左佢好多踢波意識同做人道理<br />\n佢講過起費格遜身上學識爭勝心<br />\n佢既鬥心大家有眼見<br />\n<br />\n而費格遜亦寫書講過一生培育過四位世界級球員<br />\nC朗係當中最為優秀（btw朗尼無份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n我佢諗一生應該最滿足既不過於此<br />\n亦造就今時今日永不放棄 刻苦鍛練既C朗<br />\n<br />\n（次前雲加仲話爭啲簽到C朗 想像下比雲加教既爭勝心會變成點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 奧燒同埋山齊士就係好樣板 沉既沉走既走）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1420606/org/2ea6964b93ddbddb992f179ee7539284.JPG/IbLXyUNIzwZ5CDZaY9yiyHwh-aPhRw1orq_3W66v91s?v=w800\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1420606%2Forg%2F2ea6964b93ddbddb992f179ee7539284.JPG%2FIbLXyUNIzwZ5CDZaY9yiyHwh-aPhRw1orq_3W66v91s%3Fv%3Dw800&h=46990f23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>第二位貴人：施丹</strong><br />\nC朗自己講過仙丹令佢不停進步<br />\n起皇馬轉領隊已是常事<br />\n仙丹最服到眾既一樣野係佢會跟埋落去同球員操<br />\n<br />\n之前有單野就係仙丹親自教C朗射罰球<br />\nC朗呢啲自尊心重既球員要再改進<br />\n就一定要搵過自己真心服既人<br />\n（諗下之前唔記得邊個上任時送左份入波剪輯比佢做禮物 比c朗扔左再話自己可以show次佢睇就知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n<br />\n仙丹既出現正正係C朗歲數踏入職業球員完結巔峰之時<br />\n但仙丹可以用言行一致咁讓C朗明白係時候轉變<br />\n<br />\n大家又見證佢由以前爆人、死扭<br />\n變左搶點、終結者既踢法<br />\n同時keep好body 改變踢法迎接機能退化<br />\n而且更能融入皇馬踢法得黎 發揮自己強項<br />\n<br />\n呢股既轉變同樣起佢踢葡萄牙身上見到<br />\n跑上跑落幫波唔在講 關鍵時間挺身而出 識得用唔同角色令球隊勝利 唔係淨係識得表現自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n記得有次佢起球會知道賓周啞火<br />\n突登讓左球十二碼比佢主射 亦令自己無左帶帽機會<br />\n成個心態都同以前唔同晒<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images-performgroup-com.cdn.ampproject.org/ii/w680/s/images.performgroup.com/di/library/omnisport/5/2a/cristiano-ronaldo-zinedine-zidane_69c5o166amw71i7h2sb5vj6y2.jpg?t=-1226510661&amp;quality=100&amp;w=640&amp;h=360\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-performgroup-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fii%2Fw680%2Fs%2Fimages.performgroup.com%2Fdi%2Flibrary%2Fomnisport%2F5%2F2a%2Fcristiano-ronaldo-zinedine-zidane_69c5o166amw71i7h2sb5vj6y2.jpg%3Ft%3D-1226510661%26quality%3D100%26w%3D640%26h%3D360&h=ce818ab1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nC朗一生真係有好多貴人<br />\n呢到都唔一一數出黎<br />\n<br />\n對比下另一位球王美斯<br />\n做左巴塞大佬連教練球會都比佢話<br />\n係就係球隊核心 但亦造成無張自我中心<br />\n<br />\n起母會由細踢到大既球會會就你 <br />\n但出到去國家隊唔係你話晒事啦<br />\n仲唔改變自己 只係為左表現自己<br />\n<br />\n輸左又話退出國家隊 <br />\n有機會又返返黎玩 關鍵時刻累埋球隊<br />\n對波愈沉佢仲沉過隊波<br />\n只怪佢既成長都係靠天才波 <br />\n少似C朗咁有人教佢人生 <br />\n<br />\n諗下跟巴塞時期既哥帥學到控球仲有乜？<br />\n咪就係插水同圍球證<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/3/2018/01/01/6/68ac73f592242d616ad285e6597e81da.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F3%2F2018%2F01%2F01%2F6%2F68ac73f592242d616ad285e6597e81da.jpg&h=85a68f82&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以話 美斯一日起到 阿根廷都收皮啦<br />\n擺期望落阿古路仲好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcc869e151c5bee973df77b571beaac4f2161f8e","tid":705183,"uid":79418,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T02:36:47.000Z","msg":"貴人唔一定係教練 球員都得<br />\n細哨 沙維 恩尼斯達........."},{"pid":"57246b5ab545c2a09b3d92d952a4f008b4247e37","tid":705183,"uid":33125,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T02:38:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好撚客觀<br />\n整係拎 c朗好個 d黎講<br />\n拎美斯衰個 d黎講"},{"pid":"6852741592c0dad64b1274091f005897611ca9c0","tid":705183,"uid":294,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T02:42:52.000Z","msg":"同意c朗有貴人, 但messi 無咩?<br />\n<br />\n跟哥狗點會學唔到野? sterling sane jesus 幾大進步, 破埋英超紀錄<br />\nmessi 仲有疤塞成個青訓系統<br />\n由細到大已經train到有意識, 先同隊友配合得咁好<br />\n相反, 後生c朗去到曼初期都無咩意識, 之後先有費sir教佢<br />\n<br />\n因為打國家隊唔掂, 比人抽下水, 就講到佢無人無物咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d52614b4e89ed34bc12d500a4c312d61b77d0caf","tid":705183,"uid":97080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T02:43:08.000Z","msg":"拿利又唔提"},{"pid":"580226c954350fe197980705a06eec1337cb175e","tid":705183,"uid":5971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T02:51:31.000Z","msg":"作都作好啲喇<br />\n<br />\n咁撚有鋪排<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b908d492b4792c85f9a2e90af61e5eabf002b384","tid":705183,"uid":31151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T02:54:53.000Z","msg":"講撚到美斯做埋教練果份咁 係既話pavon就一早正選啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed44914596c4b77b020720f2eb3a4d77d55dc484","tid":705183,"uid":77788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T02:56:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c08c5d4bb6749cb5210f8654e9036b50f0bfda71","tid":705183,"uid":14423,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T03:10:30.000Z","msg":"第一位費人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3528e8dfc377223f63bbfddd4b0f74c7d01b320b","tid":705183,"uid":144546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ed44914596c4b77b020720f2eb3a4d77d55dc484","tid":705183,"uid":77788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T02:56:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T03:13:30.000Z","msg":"完全無留意到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fc772a42f282bd51c6a5b53eb9b46c8b88a43bd","tid":705183,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":